Returns **Cot3** value  

**COT(int number).Cot3[int barsAgo]**

Returns **Cot4** value  

**COT(int number).Cot4[int barsAgo]**

Returns **Cot5** value  

**COT(int number).Cot5[int barsAgo]**

## Return Value

